Cuddle Pirate Theater

The Cuddle Pirates are a merry band of plushie pirates that commandeer bedt=
ime and put on a show to tell their bedtime stories, and then when everyone=
 is asleep, they steal all the comfiest pillows and softest blankies in all=
 the world, to take their fluffy plunder back to Puff-tooga, their Cuddle P=
irate Island.

One night, they swoop in on little Juniper. While dodging Mom so they remai=
n invisible, they entertain her with an acrobatic ragdoll antics show. With=
 Mom distracted across the hall doing laundry. Juniper admits to the Cuddle=
s that she is sad about her missing sock, and the Cuddle Pirates tell her a=
 bedtime story.


Bedtime Stories:

[alternate story: the Cuddle Pirates are like the tooth fairy, the crying c=
hildren are their Moby Dick and they must engage the beast to get him to sl=
eep]

--Ava and the Razor Monster (or vacuum monster)


The Fluffy Dutchman =96 This is the Pirates' ship, which also serves as a p=
illowcase for all of them.  [Their legs stick out the bottom so they can ru=
n with it when they need to escape]


Note: Cuddle pirates character designs could based on caricatures of raylan=
's uncles and grandpa's.

--
Sir Francis Drake - Sir Fuzzy Drake - English
Marco Polo - Marco Pillow - Italian
Vasco de Gama - Vasco PaJamas - Portugese/Spanish
Long John Silver - Long John Snuggle (fictional, Treasure Island)
Ferdinand Magellan - Feathernand Magellan / Portugese
Captain Kidd =96 Cashmere Kidd/Captain Kitty - Scottish
Ponce de Leon - Plushy de Leon - Spanish
--

Davy Jones - Cozy Jones - Hugsy Jones - fictional
Anne Bonny - Anne Bunny - Irish
Jean Lafitte - Jean LaFluffe - French


-----thesaurus----

downy, nuzzle, hugs, puffy, fuzzy, wooly, cashmere, velveteen

---costumes----

all pirate costumes are fuzzy pajamas

ALTERNATES CHARS:


Sir Walter Raleigh =96 Sir Wooly Raleigh
Francois l'Olonnais
Jolly Roger
Blackbeard
Samuel Bellamy - Black Sam
Black Caesar
Calico Jack
Oliver La Buse

Need Asian pirates:

Need Middle Eastern Pirates

Need African Pirates


